        <div n="219-135F">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-219-135F-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-219-135F-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-219-135F-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">To a Friend who Married a shrew&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-219-135F-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-219-135F-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-219-135F-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">By Dean Swift</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-219-135F-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-219-135F-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-219-135F-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="large-writing">Nell</hi> scolded in so loud a Din,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-2" n="2">That Will dust hardly Venture in:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-3" n="3">He mark'd the Conjugal Dispute;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-4" n="4">Nell roars incessant, Dick sat Mute:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-5" n="5">But, when he saw his friend Appear,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-6" n="6">Cry'd bravely, Patience, good my Dear.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-7" n="7">At sight of Will She brawl'd no more,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-8" n="8">But Hurry'd out &amp; Clapt the Door.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-9" n="9"><hi rend="large-writing">Why</hi> Dick! the Devill's in thy Nell,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-10" n="10">Quoth Will; thy house is worse than Hell:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-11" n="11">Why, what a Peal the jade has rung!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-12" n="12">Damn her, Why Don't You slit her Tongue?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-13" n="13">For nothing else could make cease:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-14" n="14">Dear Will, I suffer this for Peace;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-15" n="15">I never quarrel with my Wife:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-16" n="16">I bear it for A quiet Life.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-17" n="17">Scripture You know Exorts us to it;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-18" n="18">Bids us seek Peace and ensue it.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-19" n="19">Will went again to Visit Dick;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-20" n="20">And Ent'ring in the Very Nick,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-21" n="21">He saw Virago Nell belabour,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-22" n="22">W<hi rend="superscript">tḥ</hi> Dicks own staff, his peaceful Neighbour,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-23" n="23">Poor Will, who needs must Interpose,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-24" n="24">Received a brace or two of Blows.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-25" n="25">But now to make my story short,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-26" n="26">Will drew out Dick to take a quart.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-27" n="27">Why Dick, thy Wife has Dev'lish Whims;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-28" n="28">Ods buds, Why don't You break her Limbs?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-29" n="29">If she were mine, and had such Tricks,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-30" n="30">I'd teach her how to handle sticks:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-31" n="31">Z──ds I wou'd ship her for Jamaica,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-32" n="32">And truck the Carrion for Tobacco;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-33" n="33">I'd send her far Enough away──</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-34" n="34">Dear Will; but what wou'd People say?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-35" n="35">Lord! I shou'd get so ill a name,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-36" n="36">The Neighbours round wou'd cry out Shame:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-37" n="37">Dick suffer'd for his peace &amp; Credit;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-38" n="38">But, Who believ'd him when he said it?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-39" n="39">Can he who makes himself a slave</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-40" n="40">Consult his Peace, or Credit save?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-41" n="41">Dick found it by his ill Success:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-42" n="42">His quiet small, his Credit less.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-43" n="43">She serv'd him at the Usual rate;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-44" n="44">She stun'd, and then She broke his pate.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-45" n="45">And what he thought the Hardest Case;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-46" n="46">The Parish jeer'd him to his face;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-47" n="47">Those men who wore the Breeches least,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-48" n="48">Call'd him a Cuckold, fool, and Beast.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-49" n="49">At home he was Persu'd with Noise;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-50" n="50">Abroad was Pester'd with the Boys.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-51" n="51">Within his wife wou'd Break his Bones,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-52" n="52">Without they Pelted him With Stones:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-53" n="53">The Prentices Procured a Riding,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-54" n="54">To act his Patience, and her Chiding.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-55" n="55">False Patience, &amp; Mistaken Pride,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-56" n="56">There are ten thousand Dicks beside:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-57" n="57">Slaves to their quiet and good Name,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-219-135F-line-58" n="58">Are Used like Dick, and bear the Blame.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
